Package com.github._1c_syntax.bsl.parser

Interface BSLParserListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
BSLParserBaseListener
public interface BSLParserListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by BSLParser.
